{"tid":1954230,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"核動力航母羅斯福號檢驗700人，其中200人確診武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-04-01T16:19:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T05:26:22.000Z","uid":53062,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8028becdecf3cded5de20a843b4fb7ec33a94d83","tid":1954230,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T16:19:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/world/uss-theodore-roosevelt-crew-isolated-coronavirus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fworld%2Fuss-theodore-roosevelt-crew-isolated-coronavirus&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUgQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=6dec0e18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fworld%2Fuss-theodore-roosevelt-crew-isolated-coronavirus&h=508ee760\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.foxnews.com/world/uss-theodore-roosevelt-crew-isolated-coronavirus</a><br />\n<br />\nNavy 仲慢吞吞，係關島搵位置上岸安置<br />\n習近平成為史上第一個令美國核航母戰鬥群失去作戰能力的元首<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd37a055b791734c9326896eefb4b797fda563e","tid":1954230,"uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T16:22:07.000Z","msg":"Modly said the Navy has been testing 200 sailors per day on board the ship, but, &quot;that is quickly ramping up.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nAsked about the high number of infections, Modly admitted, &quot;It's a lot.&quot; He pledged &quot;100 percent&quot; testing for everyone on board.<br />\n<br />\nTo date, about 700 sailors on board have been tested, Modly said, leaving another 4,300 awaiting their fate<br />\n<br />\n每日驗200人，仲有4300人未驗"},{"pid":"ea4f2c089d188d4292e79b3dacfcf209d110fc0a","tid":1954230,"uid":303133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T16:22:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ab454be50aac9a241b18bd91391f6